## Recommended Palette for Imperium Store

Your store is not a normal shopping site. It sells **professional trading software for Indian market traders**, with products like **Imperium Option Trading Terminal** and **Imperium Investor**. So the palette should feel **dark, premium, technical, sharp, and execution-focused**, not colorful or playful. ([Imperium Store][1])

---

# Final Brand Palette

| Role                   | Color Name          |       Hex | Use                                 |
| ---------------------- | ------------------- | --------: | ----------------------------------- |
| **Main Background**    | Imperium Black Navy | `#010711` | Full page background                |
| **Section Background** | Deep Terminal Navy  | `#030B19` | Navbar, footer, large sections      |
| **Card Background**    | Panel Navy          | `#061225` | Product cards, feature cards        |
| **Card Hover**         | Cyan-Tinted Navy    | `#07172F` | Hover states, selected cards        |
| **Primary Accent**     | Imperium Cyan       | `#00CFFF` | Buttons, active links, highlights   |
| **Accent Hover**       | Bright Cyan         | `#22CFFF` | Button hover, glowing edge          |
| **Secondary Accent**   | Trading Blue        | `#00A7F0` | Gradients, icons, subtle highlights |
| **Main Text**          | Pure White          | `#FFFFFF` | Headings, product names             |
| **Body Text**          | Soft White          | `#F3F5F7` | Descriptions                        |
| **Muted Text**         | Steel Gray          | `#8A97A8` | Captions, labels, secondary info    |

