# Best CSS Variables

Use this as your website’s main color system:

```css
:root {
  /* Core backgrounds */
  --bg-main: #010711;
  --bg-section: #030B19;
  --bg-card: #061225;
  --bg-card-hover: #07172F;
  --bg-input: #081629;

  /* Brand colors */
  --brand-cyan: #00CFFF;
  --brand-cyan-bright: #22CFFF;
  --brand-cyan-deep: #00A7F0;

  /* Text */
  --text-main: #FFFFFF;
  --text-body: #F3F5F7;
  --text-muted: #8A97A8;
  --text-disabled: #526070;

  /* Borders */
  --border-soft: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  --border-cyan-soft: rgba(0, 207, 255, 0.18);
  --border-cyan: rgba(0, 207, 255, 0.35);

  /* Glow */
  --glow-cyan-soft: 0 0 18px rgba(0, 207, 255, 0.22);
  --glow-cyan-strong: 0 0 32px rgba(0, 207, 255, 0.38);

  /* Store status colors */
  --success: #00E676;
  --warning: #FFB020;
  --error: #FF4D5E;
  --info: #00CFFF;
}
```

