# Website Usage Guide

## 1. Page Background

Use this for the full site:

```css
background: #010711;
color: #F3F5F7;
```

Avoid pure black `#000000`. Your icon already has a deep navy tone, so `#010711` will look more premium.

---

## 2. Navbar

```css
background: rgba(3, 11, 25, 0.92);
border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 207, 255, 0.18);
backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
```

Navbar links:

```css
color: #8A97A8;
```

Navbar active / hover:

```css
color: #00CFFF;
```

---

## 3. Hero Section

Use a radial glow behind the hero text:

```css
background:
  radial-gradient(circle at 50% 20%, rgba(0, 207, 255, 0.12), transparent 32%),
  radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, #07172F 0%, #030B19 42%, #010711 100%);
```

This will match the icon’s dark-blue + cyan glow style.

---

## 4. Product Cards

For products like **Imperium Option Trading Terminal** and **Imperium Investor**, use this:

```css
background:
  linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(7, 23, 47, 0.95), rgba(3, 11, 25, 0.98));

border: 1px solid rgba(0, 207, 255, 0.18);
box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
```

Hover:

```css
border-color: rgba(0, 207, 255, 0.45);
box-shadow: 0 0 28px rgba(0, 207, 255, 0.18);
transform: translateY(-2px);
```

