# Text Hierarchy

| Element        |                  Color |    Weight |
| -------------- | ---------------------: | --------: |
| Hero heading   |              `#FFFFFF` | 700 / 800 |
| Product title  |              `#FFFFFF` |       700 |
| Price          | `#FFFFFF` or `#00CFFF` |       700 |
| Body text      |              `#F3F5F7` | 400 / 500 |
| Labels         |              `#8A97A8` |       500 |
| Small captions |              `#526070` |       400 |

For price, I recommend:

```css
color: #FFFFFF;
```

Then add a cyan underline, badge, or glow near it. Do not make every price cyan, or the page will become visually noisy.

